                    <msContents>
                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus target="#2r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4750GadlaGK">Gadla Gabra Krǝstos</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዜናሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ብእሴ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <persName ref="PRS12637GabraKrestos">ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</persName> 
                                ወልደ፡ <persName ref="PRS9479Theodosi">ቴዎዶስዮስ፡</persName> ንጉሠ፡ ቊስጥንጥንያ።</incipit>
                            
                            
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus target="#74r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT1526GadlaZ"/>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዜና፡ ኂሩቱ፡ ወስነ፡ ገድሉ፡ ወጽንዓ፡ ትዕግሥቱ፡ ወተሐርሞቱ፡ ለብፁዕ፡ ወለቅዱስ፡ 
                                ብእሴ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አቡነ፡ <persName ref="PRS10581Zamika">ዘሚካኤል፡</persName> ዘውእቱ፡ አረጋዊ፡ መክብበ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ዘደብረ፡ ያሬድ፡ ቀሲስ፡ 
                                ማኅሌታይ፡ ብርሃና፡ ለኢትዮጵያ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለ<persName ref="PRS4327GabraMa">ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ <roleName type="title">ንጉሥ፡</roleName>
                        </persName>  
                                ወልደ፡ <persName ref="PRS5841Kaleb">ካሌብ።</persName>
                                ፡ </incipit>
                            
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <locus target="#180v"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT2998RepCh278"/>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"> በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡  እምግብጽ፡ ፍናዋተ፡ ግዕዛን፡ ለመርሆ። ለእግረ፡ እስራኤል፡ ሙቁሕ፡ እማዕሰረ፡ ቅንየት፡ እንዘ፡ ይፈትሖ። </incipit>
                            
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        
